title: Earth Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, International, Organic, Buffet, Take-out
description: Food is 100% vegan except organic cow's milk on request for tea/coffee. Food policy listed on cafe's website. Fair trade and mostly organic. No hydrogenated fats, MSG, colorings, preservatives, or additives. Gluten free and garlic free options. Operates on basis of Buddhist ethics. Located near Arndale Shopping Centre, Northern Quarter, High Street tram stop.
